io.spine.validate

Interface FieldAwareMessage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.google.protobuf.Message, com.google.protobuf.MessageLite, com.google.protobuf.MessageLiteOrBuilder, com.google.protobuf.MessageOrBuilder

    @GeneratedMixin
 @Experimental
 @Internal
public interface FieldAwareMessage
extends com.google.protobuf.Message
    The mixin for Messages which are aware of their fields and are able to provide their values with no reflection used by Protobuf.

    This mixin is an experimental part of the framework and may be changed or removed in future.
